{"tid":1997573,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[[跑數直擊]] 全港選民登記告急！後生仔30萬未登記 九西全港最低 港島爭3萬","createTime":"2020-05-01T18:11:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T15:24:31.000Z","uid":210495,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f7b5d82b7980069096ffde6e55b63888c85429c7","tid":1997573,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:11:12.000Z","msg":"✏️13萬年輕人未登記做選民<br />\n🔍18至20歲選民登記率只有66%(逾5.6萬人)<br />\n🔍21至25歲為79.1%(逾7.2萬人)<br />\n🔍71歲以上則為76.3%(接近17.8萬人)<br />\n<br />\n📍大獲‼️全港廢老登記超過7成6<br />\n📍26-55歲選民登記全線告急唔夠7成<br />\n📍18-30歲手足有30萬未登記<br />\n📍九西37區登記率極低不足4成5<br />\n<br />\n如果你2020年7月25日前年滿18歲、或是從未登記的香港永久居民：<br />\n⁣⁣🗳 登記做選民⁣⁣：hk2020.vote<br />\n🗳 檢查選民資料：<a href=\"http://tinyurl.com/checkmyballot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftinyurl.com%2Fcheckmyballot&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1zk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=9a06f909\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://tinyurl.com/checkmyballot</a><br />\n🗳如有需要重新登記「超區」選票：<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B-p0V5EJ0D1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-p0V5EJ0D1%2F&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1zk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=4f885b38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB-p0V5EJ0D1%2F&h=7f05b9be\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B-p0V5EJ0D1/</a><br />\n⁣⁣⁣📅截止登記日：2020年5月2日⁣⁣⁣<br />\n⁣⁣<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/94999391_131160545165538_3316953060302913536_n.jpg?_nc_cat=103&amp;_nc_sid=110474&amp;_nc_oc=AQlSBepV3QQhUEaUsqMnT5poKq4xDSUVUKwObBvaYJs9sDws_Kg5_P2DQejBfhHsR6s&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=733f746ee3a8d08377fd85f3b0c57df2&amp;oe=5ED3E0BF\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F94999391_131160545165538_3316953060302913536_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D103%26_nc_sid%3D110474%26_nc_oc%3DAQlSBepV3QQhUEaUsqMnT5poKq4xDSUVUKwObBvaYJs9sDw