150","tid":1997573,"uid":114781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"聽日一齊出去派表？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:46:01.000Z","msg":"唔派form啦聽日比qr code 同學仔上網填"},{"pid":"b4c43619186d6cd287efa00215ae5f140b58a3fb","tid":1997573,"uid":298150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"我唔太識~  登記左選民, 係未同時擁有立法會同區議會投票資格?<br />\n我查過我係區議會 (第二)  即係點?"},{"pid":"0a68a486347c1cb2f9eb31ddc165fadf46c6494e","tid":1997573,"uid":36877,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c43619186d6cd287efa00215ae5f140b58a3fb","tid":1997573,"uid":298150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"我唔太識~  登記左選民, 係未同時擁有立法會同區議會投票資格?<br />\n我查過我係區議會 (第二)  即係點?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:16:36.000Z","msg":"岩㗎喇，第二即係超區<br />\n<br />\n立法會有兩票，地區同功能組別<br />\n無特別入到功能組織既普羅大眾就有得投超區<br />\n<br />\n區選唔洗再登記多次，但建議到時都check 下選民資格"},{"pid":"de7a9cff18c852b73129190b649c9063c09ad605","tid":1997573,"uid":298150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c43619186d6cd287efa00215ae5f140b58a3fb","tid":1997573,"uid":298150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"我唔太識~  登記左選民, 係未同時擁有立法會同區議會投票資格?<br />\n我查過我係區議會 (第二)  即係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:19:15.000Z","msg":"睇完維基~ 功能界別 當中有5席 區議會 (第二) , 可以由現任區議員當中參選香港登記選民一人一票選出五個議席?"},{"pid":"f0b9f6b48915bbaf993a7f88797c9d697543c129","tid":1997573,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"132a8eb8c59f18e0398566e7af1d9b9a14d4d150","tid":1997573,"uid":114781,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T18:25:32.000Z","msg":"聽日一齊出去派表？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:26:40.000Z","msg":"（緊急最後一日）用電腦填表分人手:<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BXvBOxL5hcbi8Isj2ijkdmwcKOQX9BFqfdud_VaEbGU/edit?usp=sharing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fspreadsheets%2Fd%2F1BXvBOxL5hcbi8Isj2ijkdmwcKOQX9BFqfdud_VaEbGU%2Fedit%3Fusp%3Dsharing&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw1zk5r7V16zLonem%2BWgH46Yg%3D&h=2e5ebedc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1BXvBOxL5hcbi8Isj2ijkdmwcKOQX9BFqfdud_VaEbGU/edit?usp=sharing</a><br />\n<br />\n太多人去咗派但冇填，依幾日去咗邊間就填一填（見到其他考場有區議員做過都填埋），5月2號我哋盡量去未有人做過嘅學校<br />\n係可以派嘅學校隔離填名<br />\n如果冇電腦填嘅可以叫喺度叫其他手足幫你填"},{"pid":"f81f4d428b031afd733e9c1b93f806ce1de9b1c5","tid":1997573,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:27:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099b74ba38e39bac5fb18a8500d39da1fb0e5386","tid":1997573,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de7a9cff18c852b73129190b649c9063c09ad605","tid":1997573,"uid":298150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b4c43619186d6cd287efa00215ae5f140b58a3fb","tid":1997573,"uid":298150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:06:16.000Z","msg":"我唔太識~  登記左選民, 係未同時擁有立法會同區議會投票資格?<br />\n我查過我係區議會 (第二)  即係點?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:19:15.000Z","msg":"睇完維基~ 功能界別 當中有5席 區議會 (第二) , 可以由現任區議員當中參選香港登記選民一人一票選出五個議席?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:27:43.000Z","msg":"即係你有一票地區 一票超區<br />\n用16年港島做例子<br />\n即係<br />\n你一票可以投許智峯<br />\n一票可以投鄺仔"},{"pid":"a0942be05e5bec302455db768e41b04883fd8d69","tid":1997573,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:39:47.000Z","msg":"tuituitui"},{"pid":"b6d2c003f20ba3eb3a5d28357a94508fbea05e59","tid":1997573,"uid":210495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:58:42.000Z","msg":"tuituitui"},{"pid":"abfb300de32307913a85b7aae95c973fa23a5aea","tid":1997573,"uid":58803,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T19:59:43.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ae2d12827b530dd90614916234c43b13dc6063fa","tid":1997573,"uid":13281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2